{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We want to be friends.

296
00:36:18,218 --> 00:36:19,549
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Where's my doll?

