314
00:37:45,263 --> 00:37:47,504
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}How about Teddy instead?

315
00:37:47,682 --> 00:37:50,344
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}No. That's all right.

316
00:37:53,354 --> 00:37:55,310
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}- Did you lose a tooth?
