328
00:39:05,093 --> 00:39:06,583
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Kim, have you seen my razor?

329
00:39:07,762 --> 00:39:09,218
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We have to leave in five minutes.

330
00:39:09,305 --> 00:39:11,637
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}- Yeah. Have you seen my razor?
